OL,3,CPlan Bee: 180,000 bees rescued from
OL,4,Croof of Inverness home
OL,6,FWatch as plasterboard is stripped away
OL,7,Fto reveal around 180,000 bees living
OL,8,Fin the roof of a Scottish home
OL,10,FBy Daniel Boal, ITV News Producer
OL,12,FThree hives, 180,000 bees, and a whole
OL,13,Flot of honey, is what a beekeeper
OL,14,Ffound when he was called to a home in
OL,15,FInverness.
OL,17,FThe owner of the home knew he had a
OL,18,Fbee infestation in the house - but
OL,19,Fdidn't quite know the extent of it
OL,20,Funtil he climbed some scaffolding to
OL,21,Fbe greeted by a swarm of bees.
