OL,3,CPlan Bee: 180,000 bees rescued from
OL,4,Croof of Inverness home
OL,6,FAfter calling in the Loch Ness Honey
OL,7,FCompany, beekeeper Andrew Card set
OL,8,Fabout using thermal imaging to work
OL,9,Fout just how many bees had been living
OL,10,Fin the roof of the home.
OL,12,FTearing away plasterboard in the spare
OL,13,Fbedroom of the property revealed three
OL,14,Fhives, each containing around 60,000
OL,15,Fbees.
OL,17,FThe oldest of the three hives is
OL,18,Fthought to be at least seven years
OL,19,Fold, while the other two are thought
OL,20,Fto have embedded more recently.
