OL,4,Croof of Inverness home
OL,6,FMaking use of a special hoover or "Bee
OL,7,FVac", around half the bees in each of
OL,8,Fthe hives were gently sucked away.
OL,10,FMr Card then began removing the
OL,11,Fwaxcomb containing the rest of the
OL,12,Fcolony.
OL,14,FWhile the honey found alongside the
OL,15,F180,000 bees won't be packed up and
OL,16,Fsold by the Loch Ness Honey Company,
OL,17,Fit will sustain the bees that were
OL,18,Frescued from the home.
