OL,3,CPlan Bee: 180,000 bees rescued from
OL,4,Croof of Inverness home
OL,6,FAfter being relocated to new hives,
OL,7,Fthey will be tested for diseases and
OL,8,Fnurtured to be strong enough for
OL,9,Fwinter.
OL,11,FMr Card told ITV News he hopes it will
OL,12,Fbecome a "full circle moment" and that
OL,13,Feventually the bees he had rescued
OL,14,Fwill produce honey for his business.
OL,16,FWith an average lifespan of between
OL,17,Ftwo to three years, queen bees can lay
OL,18,Fup to 2,000 honey bee eggs in a single
OL,19,Fday.
